## Server/headless strain: no desktop environment package at all.
## base.list.chroot already covers openssh-server; Docker/Netdata are
## intentionally left to modes/server/setup/*.sh, not baked in here --
## same lean-image philosophy as iso/README.md's main scope decision.
## (No packages of its own right now -- this file exists so build.sh has
## something to copy in and the strain selection mechanism stays uniform
## across all 6 strains rather than special-casing "none".)
